<br />
theres a spot you can coh to if you not kos to CoV. The spot is on the catwalk up the stairs around the corner from Ikitar and RIGHT b4 Aaryonar. Theres these little drake things (we call them chickens) that are on cov faction so coh the non kos people first but its a pretty good spot to start at Aary anyway.
<br />

<br />

<br />
